<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-437-008  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 437 008.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  July 10 1989 v6 n27 p29(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Text-retrieval system accesses wire services. (GescanInternational Inc.) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Ballou, Melinda-Carol.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Gescan International Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   General Electric GESCAN 3.7 (Information retrieval system)(product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionInformation Storage and RetrievalOn-Line Searching.andO;Feature:   illustrationphotograph.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Text-Retrieval System Accesses Wire ServicesandM;RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C.andP;  -- Gescan International has released version3.7 of its Gescan text-retrieval system, which enables users to pullinformation off wire services and do &quot;real-time&quot; searching, company officialssaid.andM;&quot;This new version provides the capability to watch information as it comesoff the line and attach it to your interest query so that it's routed to youin less than a second after it comes off the wire,&quot; said Dave Morris, vicepresident of marketing for Gescan.andM;&quot;We have included in our system the ability to handle ANPA [AmericanNewspaper Publishers Association] formats so that it will take the incomingstory or them off the wire and automatically determine the date, the authorand the headline, and field all that information,&quot; Morris said.andM;&quot;So if you want to look for 'Bush' listed only in the headlines but notelsewhere in the story, it will send you those stories,&quot; Morris added.andM;Gescan 3.7 performs a sequential search, reading every character and everyline.andM;&quot;You don't have to do Boolean operators or proximity if you don't want to,&quot;Morris said.andP;  &quot;There's a thesaurus capability that will bring in otherrelated terms.&quot;andM;The new release of Gescan accepts input from wire services following the ANPAWire Service Transmission Guideline and standard government message formats,including DOI 103, Janap 128 and ACP 127.andM;Other Features IncludedandM;The release also provides enhanced optical character recognition (OCR)interfaces, a new report generator, improved manipulation of search results(including new sort functions and display formats), and improved OCR softwarefor faster loading of hard-copy documents into a database, the officialssaid.andM;Gescan 3.7 is available now for DEC systems running VMS 5.1.andP;  PRices for thenew version range from $25,000 to $40,000, depending on CPU.andM;For more information, Gescan International Inc. can be contacted at P.O. Box12599, Research Triangle Park, N.C.andP;  27709, (919) 460-3100.andO;</TEXT></DOC>